# Runtime artifacts written by Claude Code into the repo-root .claude/ dir.
# Root-anchored (/.claude/) so nested test fixtures with a .claude/ subdir
# are unaffected. Specific patterns rather than a blanket dir ignore so that
# intentional project config (.claude/settings.json, commands/, etc.) can be
# tracked without --force if ever needed.
/.claude/*.lock
/.claude/*.tmp
